(**The 3-Step Validation Framework**) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 9 Tf
36 248 Td
0.102 0.102 0.102 rg
() Tj
ET
BT
/F1 9 Tf
36 237 Td
0.102 0.102 0.102 rg
(I've helped 20+ founders validate ideas. The ones who succeed follow a simple pattern:) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 9 Tf
36 226 Td
0.102 0.102 0.102 rg
() Tj
ET
BT
/F1 9 Tf
36 215 Td
0.102 0.102 0.102 rg
(**Step 1: Talk to 10 people \(week 1\)**) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 9 Tf
36 204 Td
0.102 0.102 0.102 rg
(Don't ask "Would you use this?" People say yes to everything.) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 9 Tf
36 193 Td
0.102 0.102 0.102 rg
(Instead, ask: "What's the biggest pain you have in [domain]?") Tj
ET
BT
/F1 9 Tf
36 182 Td
0.102 0.102 0.102 rg
(Listen for patterns. If 5+ people mention the same problem, you've found market need.) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 9 Tf
36 171 Td
0.102 0.102 0.102 rg
() Tj
ET
BT
/F1 9 Tf
36 160 Td
0.102 0.102 0.102 rg
(**Step 2: Pre-sell \(week 2\)**) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 9 Tf
36 149 Td
0.102 0.102 0.102 rg
(Can you actually sell this idea before it exists?) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 9 Tf
36 138 Td
0.102 0.102 0.102 rg
(Offer a discount for early access. "I'm building X. Would you pay $50/month for it?") Tj
ET
BT
/F1 9 Tf
36 127 Td
0.102 0.102 0.102 rg
(If people won't commit even with a 50% discount, you don't have a market.) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 9 Tf
36 116 Td
0.102 0.102 0.102 rg
() Tj
ET
BT
/F1 9 Tf
36 105 Td
0.102 0.102 0.102 rg
(**Step 3: Interview the "yes" people \(week 2\)**) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 9 Tf
36 94 Td
0.102 0.102 0.102 rg
(Talk to the 2-3 people who said yes.) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 9 Tf
36 83 Td
0.102 0.102 0.102 rg
(Ask what they'd want, what they'd pay, what problems they'd want solved first.) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 9 Tf
36 72 Td
0.102 0.102 0.102 rg
(These conversations give you the roadmap.) Tj
ET
BT
